Entra Emulator is an independent, clean-room implementation of the publicly
documented Microsoft Entra ID protocol surface (OpenID Connect / OAuth 2.0,
Microsoft identity platform v2.0 endpoint shapes), built from Microsoft's
public documentation and RFCs.

